data.description: Lovely Inglewood single story home is in the heart of town, located near Downtown, Midtown, & Olde Town with walkability to Governor's Park as well as loads of restaurants & shopping in the Magnolia/Apalachee Parkway area ~ Convenient in-town living with 1960's charm ~ 3 Bedrooms ~ 1.5 Baths ~ Home sits on a quarter acre lot ~ Original hardwood floors throughout ~ Separate Family Room in rear of the home has low maintenance tile floors & opens to large, new deck in backyard ~ Roof & water heater replaced in 2018 ~ Kitchen has brand new gas stove & range hood 2023 ~ Complete interior freshly painted & new front door ~ Indoor Laundry room, washer & dryer included ~ Carport for one car, plus driveway ~ Check out the virtual tour for additional photos ~
